## 默认环境变量配置（直接使用local环境配置）
# 使用全局环境配置文件 http-client.env.json
# 请在IntelliJ IDEA中选择对应环境: local/dev/test/gateway
# 登录成功后会自动更新token到环境变量中

### 1. 获取设备规模统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/dashboard/device-scale
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: 184717008866115584

### 2. 获取累计设备接入数趋势
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/dashboard/cumulative-device-count-trend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 3. 获取设备隐患列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/dashboard/device-hazards
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 4. 获取预测性隐患数量趋势
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/dashboard/predictive-hazard-trend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 5. 获取待处理隐患工单列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/dashboard/pending-hazard-work-orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 6. 获取告警列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/dashboard/alarm-list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 7. 获取设备故障检测统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/dashboard/device-fault-detection
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 天工 => 设备信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/dashboard/device-info-all
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: 184717008866115584

{
